  <brief_title>Optimising Outpatient Care in Mild to Moderate Psoriasis (PSO-TOP)</brief_title>
  <acronym>PSO-TOP</acronym>
  <official_title>Optimising Outpatient Care in Mild to Moderate Psoriasis by a Newly Developed 'Topical Treatment Optimising Programme' - an International Study Using Daivobet®/Dovobet® Gel</official_title>
